{
  "dashboard": {
    "id": null,
    "title": "IDS Lab - Simple Log Monitor",
    "tags": ["ids", "snort", "logs"],
    "style": "dark",
    "timezone": "browser",
    "refresh": "5s",
    "time": {
      "from": "now-30m",
      "to": "now"
    },
    "panels": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "Live Snort Logs",
        "type": "logs",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "{job=\"snort\"}",
            "refId": "A",
            "datasource": {
              "type": "loki",
              "uid": "loki"
            }
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "showTime": true,
          "showLabels": false,
          "showCommonLabels": false,
          "wrapLogMessage": false,
          "prettifyLogMessage": false,
          "enableLogDetails": true,
          "dedupStrategy": "none",
          "sortOrder": "Descending"
        },
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 12,
          "w": 24,
          "x": 0,
          "y": 0
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "title": "Log Volume Over Time",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate({job=\"snort\"}[1m])",
            "refId": "A",
            "datasource": {
              "type": "loki",
              "uid": "loki"
            }
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": {
              "mode": "palette-classic"
            },
            "custom": {
              "drawStyle": "line",
              "lineInterpolation": "linear",
              "barAlignment": 0,
              "lineWidth": 2,
              "fillOpacity": 10,
              "gradientMode": "none",
              "spanNulls": false,
              "insertNulls": false,
              "showPoints": "auto",
              "pointSize": 5
            }
          }
        },
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 8,
          "w": 24,
          "x": 0,
          "y": 12
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "title": "Snort Status",
        "type": "stat",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "count({job=\"snort\"})",
            "refId": "A",
            "datasource": {
              "type": "loki",
              "uid": "loki"
            }
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": {
              "mode": "thresholds"
            },
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "color": "red",
                  "value": null
                },
                {
                  "color": "green",
                  "value": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            "mappings": [
              {
                "options": {
                  "0": {
                    "text": "NO DATA"
                  }
                },
                "type": "value"
              }
            ],
            "unit": "short"
          }
        },
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 6,
          "w": 8,
          "x": 0,
          "y": 20
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "title": "Lab Instructions",
        "type": "text",
        "options": {
          "content": "## IDS Lab Dashboard\n\n**To see data in this dashboard:**\n\n1. Run attacks from the attacker container:\n   ```\n   docker exec -it attacker bash\n   /scripts/attack_menu.sh\n   ```\n\n2. Monitor Snort logs:\n   ```\n   docker logs -f ids\n   ```\n\n3. Check log files:\n   ```\n   ls -la logs/\n   ```\n\n**Available Attacks:**\n- ICMP Flood\n- SYN Flood \n- HTTP Flood\n- Port Scanning\n- Web Application Attacks\n\n**Snort Configuration:**\n- Rules: `/snort/rules/`\n- Config: `/snort/config/`\n- Logs: `/logs/`",
          "mode": "markdown"
        },
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 6,
          "w": 16,
          "x": 8,
          "y": 20
        }
      }
